graph TD
    A[User] -->|Uploads User Story| B(FastAPI Endpoint<br/>/generate)

    subgraph "API Server"
        B --> C[Embed User Story<br/>using Sentence Transformer]
        C --> D[Query Qdrant<br/>for similar code chunks]
        D --> E[Build Prompt<br/>with context + story]
        E --> F[Call OpenAI API]
        F --> G[Parse Generated Code<br/>into file list]
        G --> H[Create ZIP archive<br/>in memory]
    end

    subgraph "Vector Database"
        I[(Qdrant Collection<br/>codebase_index)]
        D --> I
    end

    subgraph "Embedding Model"
        J[BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5]
        C --> J
    end

    subgraph "LLM"
        K[OpenAI GPT-4 / GPT-3.5]
        F --> K
    end

    H --> L[Return ZIP file<br/>to User]
    L --> A